1110:
SELECT uses_knowledge_graph, COUNT(evaluation_metric) AS count_evaluation_metric 
FROM cspaper 
WHERE reasoning_depth = 'multi-hop' 
GROUP BY uses_knowledge_graph;
1210:
SELECT reasoning_depth, SUM(baseline_amount) AS sum_baseline_amount 
FROM cspaper 
WHERE retrieval_method = 'Web Search; Dense Retrieval' AND use_agent = 'No' 
GROUP BY reasoning_depth;
1310:
SELECT data_modality, AVG(baseline_amount) AS avg_baseline_amount 
FROM cspaper 
WHERE application_domain != 'Education' OR use_agent = 'Yes' 
GROUP BY data_modality;
1410:
SELECT data_modality, AVG(baseline_amount) AS avg_baseline_amount 
FROM cspaper 
WHERE use_agent = 'Yes' AND retrieval_method != 'Web Search; Dense Retrieval' AND data_modality != 'Table; Text' 
GROUP BY data_modality;
1510:
SELECT retrieval_method, SUM(baseline_amount) AS sum_baseline_amount 
FROM cspaper 
WHERE uses_reranker = 'No' OR performance_on_hotpotqa = 'KILT-EM: 27.3 (T5-Base); KILT-EM: 31.1 (T5-XL)' OR baseline = 'Traditional RAG' 
GROUP BY retrieval_method;
1610:
SELECT uses_knowledge_graph, COUNT(reasoning_depth) AS count_reasoning_depth 
FROM cspaper 
WHERE (baseline = 'e5-base-v2; gpt-2' AND topic = 'SFT') OR (data_modality = 'Image; Table; Text' AND topic != 'SFT') 
GROUP BY uses_knowledge_graph;
